WEBVTT

00:00.550 --> 00:06.020
When I was being held, I felt like a real man was holding me.

00:06.480 --> 00:10.440
I felt warm inside and was excited.

00:11.160 --> 00:16.190
I don’t know if it was because I felt like Dad was holding me or because I was imagining someone else.

00:16.520 --> 00:17.420
I don’t know.

00:17.720 --> 00:20.140
This feels good, though.

00:20.560 --> 00:23.520
Is this what I wanted my real Dad to do with me?

00:24.240 --> 00:27.410
I just wanted someone to protect me.
